short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Integration with TriSys Recruitment CRM/ATS Database.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TriSys is a recruitment customer relationship management system, and this extension allows recruiters to pull data from web sites and to lookup CRM data when visiting web sites.
